00:26:05.280 --> 00:26:06.600
They sum to 2.

00:26:06.600 --> 00:26:08.610
So you get that.

00:26:08.610 --> 00:26:15.020
The point is that it's a
pretty simple transformation

00:26:15.020 --> 00:26:18.740
to think about the
