00:26:18.740 --> 00:26:23.570
into a sequence of amplitudes.

00:26:23.570 --> 00:26:26.480
So if you choose--

00:26:26.480 --> 00:26:27.015
let's see.

00:26:27.015 --> 00:26:30.350
So if you choose k
to be even, then I've

00:26:30.350 --> 00:26:34.435
got an integer multiple of 2 pi.

