00:27:04.680 --> 00:27:14.847
So we get that ak is 1 over
j pi k, k odd, 0 otherwise.

00:27:17.590 --> 00:27:18.310
OK.

00:27:18.310 --> 00:27:20.840
And then we can just sort of
run down through the list.

00:27:20.840 --> 00:27:23.590
We'll see in a minute why this
particular list of properties

00:27:23.590 --> 00:27:24.790
is interesting.

00:27:24.790 --> 00:27:27.230
So a sub k is 0 if k is even?

